{
  "page": "The Liddle",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the head of House Liddle, see <a href=\"/index.php/Torren_Liddle\" title=\"Torren Liddle\">Torren Liddle</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Liddle\" title=\"House Liddle\"><img alt=\"House Liddle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/House_Liddle.svg/50px-House_Liddle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/House_Liddle.svg/75px-House_Liddle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/House_Liddle.svg/100px-House_Liddle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">The Liddle</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Liddle\" title=\"House Liddle\"><img alt=\"House Liddle.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/House_Liddle.svg/50px-House_Liddle.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f6/House_Liddle.svg/75px-House_Liddle.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f6/House_Liddle.svg/100px-House_Liddle.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Bran_Stark_and_the_Liddle_by_Effemar.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bran Stark and the Liddle by Effemar.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/64/Bran_Stark_and_the_Liddle_by_Effemar.png/350px-Bran_Stark_and_the_Liddle_by_Effemar.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/64/Bran_Stark_and_the_Liddle_by_Effemar.png/525px-Bran_Stark_and_the_Liddle_by_Effemar.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/64/Bran_Stark_and_the_Liddle_by_Effemar.png/700px-Bran_Stark_and_the_Liddle_by_Effemar.png 2x\" /></a><div>Bran Stark and the Liddle, by Effemar ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Liddle\" title=\"House Liddle\">House Liddle</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountain_clans\" title=\"Northern mountain clans\">Northern mountain clans</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>The Liddle</b> is a traveler in the <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountains\" title=\"Northern mountains\">northern mountains</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a> presumes he is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Liddle\" title=\"House Liddle\">House Liddle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His name is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Behind_the_Scenes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behind the Scenes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Liddle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The Liddle is generous with food and shelter. His <a href=\"/index.php/Squirrel\" title=\"Squirrel\">squirrelskin</a> cloak is clasped with a <a href=\"/index.php/Pine\" title=\"Pine\">pinecone</a> made of <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Bronze\" title=\"Bronze\">bronze</a>, and he carries a knife and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Liddle\" title=\"House Liddle\">green and white</a> cloth.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Liddle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The man learned the phrase \"<a href=\"/index.php/Raven\" title=\"Raven\">dark wings</a>, dark words\" from his mother, who died nine years ago.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Liddle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Liddle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>One day when <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Hodor</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a> are traveling through the <a href=\"/index.php/Northern_mountains\" title=\"Northern mountains\">northern mountains</a> toward the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>, a burst of freezing rain makes them look for shelter. Bran's <a href=\"/index.php/Direwolf\" title=\"Direwolf\">direwolf</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a> finds a shallow cave behind a <a href=\"/index.php/Sentinel\" title=\"Sentinel\">sentinel</a> tree, but when they enter, they find it already occupied. However, the traveler invites them to share the shelter of the cave and the warmth of his fire. The man does not ask their names, nor gives his. Bran assumes he is a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Liddle\" title=\"House Liddle\">Liddle</a> because of the man's <a href=\"/index.php/Pine\" title=\"Pine\">pinecone</a>-shaped cloak clasp, however, and the man is implied to recognize Bran and his direwolf as <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Starks</a>. The Liddle offers oatcakes, blood sausage, and <a href=\"/index.php/Ale\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ale\">ale</a> to Bran's party. He informs them that <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> are in the <a href=\"/index.php/Wolfswood\" title=\"Wolfswood\">wolfswood</a>, and he looks at Bran and Summer after warning that the <a href=\"/index.php/Ramsay_Snow\" title=\"Ramsay Snow\">Bastard</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard%27s_boys\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard&#39;s boys\">boys</a> are hunting along the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsroad\" title=\"Kingsroad\">kingsroad</a>. He also mentions the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_ranging\" title=\"Great ranging\">great ranging</a> into the <a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">haunted forest</a> by the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Liddle departs before Bran and his companions wake in the morning, but he leaves them a sausage and twelve oatcakes containing pinenuts or blackberries, wrapped in green and white cloth. Bran has one of each oatcake, and greatly enjoys the food. He thinks that when <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a> returns to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>, he will pay back House Liddle a hundredfold.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Liddle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Come in and warm yourselves. There's stone enough to keep the rain off all our heads.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;The Liddle to <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a>'s party</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Liddle</b>: It was different when there was a <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Stark</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>. But the <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">old wolf's</a> dead and <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">young one's</a> gone south to play the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">game of thrones</a>, and all that's left us is <a href=\"/index.php/Capture_of_Winterfell\" title=\"Capture of Winterfell\">the ghosts</a>.<br />\n</p><p><b>Jojen</b>: The wolves will come again.<br />\n<b>Liddle</b>: And how would you be knowing, boy?<br />\n<b>Jojen</b>: I <a href=\"/index.php/Greendream\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Greendream\">dreamed</a> it.<br />\n<b>Liddle</b>: Some nights I dream of me mother that I buried nine years past, but when I wake, she's not come back to us.<br />\n</p>\n<b>Jojen</b>: There are dreams and dreams, my lord.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;The Liddle and <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p> One day there would be <a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">Starks</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> again, he told himself, and then he'd send for <a href=\"/index.php/House_Liddle\" title=\"House Liddle\">the Liddles</a> and pay them back a hundredfold for every nut and berry.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behind_the_Scenes\">Behind the Scenes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Liddle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Behind the Scenes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>According to a semi-canon source, <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> has confirmed the man is a Liddle.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Liddle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.7</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, Bran II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Westeros.org: <a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/28614-mysterious-character-the-liddle/#comment-1394097\">Mysterious Character: \"the Liddle\"</a>, June 11, 2008</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403235120\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.115 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.326 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1389/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10909/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 9454/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1797/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2814/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.190/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.64 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  306.057      1 -total\n 80.66%  246.855      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 80.12%  245.203      1 Template:Infobox\n 10.23%   31.301      1 Template:For\n  9.98%   30.559     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  7.48%   22.880      8 Template:Ref\n  4.92%   15.053      8 Template:Ref/core\n  3.47%   10.635      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.24%    6.860      3 Template:Quote\n  0.83%    2.545      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:32248-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403235119 and revision id 330383\n -->\n",
